data.description: Presenting this lovely 3-bed, 2-bath Eastlake home. VA/FHA-approved, single-floor layout, fireplace, two parking spaces, and storage. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, featuring a newer stainless steel gas stove and microwave in the kitchen, creating a chef's delight. The bathrooms have also been enhanced with new floors, sinks, and mirrors, adding a touch of modern elegance to the space. Community amenities: pool, tennis court, lagoon, walking trails, 3 pools and club house. No Mello-Roos.Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the desirable Eastlake community of Chula Vista. This VA-approved property boasts a fireplace, convenient single-floor layout, perfect for easy living.   Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, featuring a brand new stainless steel gas stove and microwave in the kitchen, creating a chef's delight. The bathrooms have also been enhanced with new floors, sinks, and mirrors, adding a touch of modern elegance to the space.  Outside, the community offers an array of resort-style amenities, including a sparkling pool for relaxation, a tennis court for active pursuits, a serene lagoon for peaceful moments, and picturesque walking trails for enjoying the outdoors.  With the added benefit of no mello roos and two parking spaces, this home presents a wonderful opportunity for comfortable, low-maintenance living in a sought-after location. Don't miss the chance to make this Eastlake gem your own!
